  "detailed_description": "In Gravitorium, you harness the power of rotating gravity!  A platformer without a jump button, rotate the world around you to maneuver through challenging precision platforming and puzzle stages as you make your way back to your home planet.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>100+ levels with many different obstacles to overcome<br></li><li>Beautiful pixel art<br></li><li>Awesome cinematics<br></li><li>Fast, technical gameplay - perfect for speedrunning!<br></li><li>Time trial mode with a Steam leaderboard<br></li><li>Unlockable skins<br></li><li>A definitely human, one-eyed hero</li></ul><br><strong>Surf alien technology!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655920/extras/530589f272a7a99d9fc022df98e66126.poster.avif?t=1736862616\" width=474 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655920/extras/530589f272a7a99d9fc022df98e66126.webm?t=1736862616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655920/extras/530589f272a7a99d9fc022df98e66126.mp4?t=1736862616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Manipulate objects around you!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655920/extras/adf43e008afb1d5327854363e9afe19e.poster.avif?t=1736862616\" width=474 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655920/extras/adf43e008afb1d5327854363e9afe19e.webm?t=1736862616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655920/extras/adf43e008afb1d5327854363e9afe19e.mp4?t=1736862616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Many different obsta